Charles F. Marcy



Mr. Charles F. Marcy is on the Board of Directors at Farmer Brothers Co. and B&G Foods, Inc. Mr. Marcy was previously employed as Chief Executive Officer by Turtle Mountain LLC, President, Chief Executive Officer & Director by Healthy Food Holdings, Inc., President, Chief Executive Officer & Director by Creamiser Products Corp., President, Chief Executive Officer & Director by SealRight Co., Inc., President by Golden Grain Macaroni Co., President by National Dairy Products Corp., a Principal by Marcy & Partners, Inc., President & Chief Executive Officer by Van's International Foods, Inc., and a Trustee by Washington & Jefferson College. He received his undergraduate degree from Washington & Jefferson College and an MBA from Harvard Business School.



